title: Saturday Night Live Season 12 Complete
description:
SNL Season 12 (1986-1987)

Saturday Night Live Went Back Up After The Return Of Lorne Michaels.

The Cast Memembers We're Funnierer As It Should Be.

Dana Carvey,Phil Hartman,Jan Hooks,Victoria Jackson,Kevin Nealon Joins The Cast Along With Nora Dunn,Jon Lovitz,And Dennis Miller.

Malcolm Jamal Warner Did A Great Job On The Sketch Of The Crosby Show (A Parody To The Cosby Show.)

The Cast Memembers Also Did An Alternate Ending To The Movie It's A Wonderful Life On December 20th 1986 Show.

So If You Want To See This. Then Watch Saturday Night Live Season 12.
